targets.query: SELECT "waiting", "active", "done"  FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" = 'users') AND $timeFilter
SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE $timeFilter and "mean" <= 800 and "status" = 'ok' and "request" = 'allRequests'
SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE $timeFilter and "mean" > 800 and "mean" <= 1200 and "status" = 'ok' and "request" = 'allRequests'
SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE $timeFilter and "mean" > 1200 and "status" = 'ok' and "request" = 'allRequests'
SELECT sum("count") FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE $timeFilter and "status" = 'ko' and "request" = 'allRequests'

SELECT 
   sum("count") AS "Total",
   min("min") AS "Min", 
   percentile("percentiles50", 50) AS "50th pct", 
   percentile("percentiles75", 75) AS "75th pct", 
   percentile("percentiles95", 95) AS "95th pct", 
   percentile("percentiles99", 99) AS "99th pct", 
   max("max") AS "Max", 
   mean("mean") AS "Mean" 
FROM 
   /^$Prefix$/
WHERE 
   "status" = 'all' AND
    $timeFilter
GROUP BY 
   "request"
SELECT sum("count") AS "OK" FROM "$db" WHERE "status" = 'ok' AND  "simulation" = '$profile' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY  "request"
SELECT sum("count") AS "OK" FROM "$db" WHERE "status" = 'ok' AND  "simulation" = '$profile' AND $timeFilter GROUP BY  "request"
SELECT last("count") FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" = 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'all') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY time(1s)
SELECT "percentiles95" FROM "PTA7" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT "percentiles99" FROM "$db" WHERE ("request" <> 'allRequests') AND $timeFilter and "simulation" = '$profile' GROUP BY "request"
SELECT "count" FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" = 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ok') AND $timeFilter
SELECT count FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE $timeFilter AND ("request" != 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ko') and "simulation" = '$profile' group by time(1s)
SELECT mean("value") FROM "measurement" WHERE $timeFilter GROUP BY time($__interval) fill(null)
SELECT count/$writeperiod FROM "$db" WHERE $timeFilter AND ("request" != 'allRequests' AND "status" = 'ko') and "simulation" = '$profile' group by request
SELECT "percentiles50" FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" <> 'allRequests') AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "request"
SELECT mean("active") FROM "$db.users" WHERE "request" != 'allUsers' AND $timeFilter and "simulation" = '$profile' GROUP BY time(1s), "simulation"
SELECT "percentiles95" FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" <> 'allRequests' AND "request" =~ /^$request$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "/^$request$/"
SELECT "percentiles99" FROM /^$Prefix$/ WHERE ("request" <> 'allRequests' AND "request" =~ /^$request$/) AND $timeFilter GROUP BY "/^$request$/"
SELECT count/$writeperiod FROM "$db" WHERE $timeFilter AND ("request" = '${request}' AND "status" = 'ok') and "simulation" = '$profile' group by request
SELECT count/$writeperiod FROM "$db" WHERE $timeFilter AND ("request" = '${request}' AND "status" = 'ko') and "simulation" = '$profile' group by request
SELECT "percentiles50" FROM "$db" WHERE ("request" = '${request}') AND $timeFilter and "simulation" = '$profile' GROUP BY "request"

list.definition: SHOW TAG VALUES from /^$Prefix$/ WITH KEY = "request"  WHERE ("request" <> 'allRequests' AND "request" <> 'users')
